classics.title: Classics
classics.description: Get your nostalgia fix with these timeless gems from the Golden Age of Hollywood.

7946.title: Crime Boss
7946.description: A small-time hood's rise in the ranks of a Mafia crime family leads to a bloody showdown with the boss of all bosses!

7976.title: The Narcotic Story
7976.description: Get ready for a roller-coaster trip of emotion with this campy collection from the golden age of Hollywood! Originally intended to warn America's youth of the perils of drugs, sex, and alcohol, these outlandish and unintentionally hilarious tales have heartache, tragedy, crime, and even insanity, lurking around every corner!

8774.title: Bride of the Gorilla
8774.description: In the jungle, the wife of a plantation owner is terrorized by a rampaging gorilla, who turns out to be her voodoo-cursed husband.

9362.title: Knives of the Avenger
9362.description: A knife throwing Viking warrior protects a young peasant woman and her son from an evil man seeking to become king.

9374.title: The Master Touch
9374.description: A safe-cracker released from prison plans one more heist and then retirement.

9401.title: Spartacus and the Ten Gladiators
9401.description: The story of Spartacus and 10 other gladiators, all of whom fought back against the Roman coliseum sport.

11528.title: Murder At The Baskervilles
11528.description: Holmes and Watson are invited to stay at the estate of their old friend Sir Baskerville. Shortly after their arrival, they are asked to help solve the mysterious disappearance of a racing horse.

51106.title: Go Ask Alice
51106.description: Inadvertently, a 14-year-old girl in the late American 1960's is sucked into an odyssey of sex and drugs. She eventually seeks help.

262776.title: Something to Sing About
262776.description: A New York bandleader journeys to Hollywood when he is offered a contract with a studio, but he is determined to do things his way and not theirs.

262779.title: The Little Princess
262779.description: After her father leaves for the war, a young girl is sent to a strict all-girls boarding school. Will she learn to enjoy her bleak new environment?

279481.title: You Only Live Once
279481.description: Paroled through the efforts of his sweetheart and her public defender employer, Eddie Taylor resolves to go straight and live down the stigma of being a three-time loser.

287497.title: Godzilla, King of the Monsters!
287497.description: A 400-foot dinosaur-like beast, awoken from undersea hibernation off the Japanese coast by atomic-bomb testing, attacks Tokyo.

291182.title: Black Magic
291182.description: Based on a novel by Alexandre Dumas, Black Magic stars Orson Welles as the 18th century master hypnotist and charismatic charlatan Cagliostro.

294873.title: Three Came Home
294873.description: The true story of Agnes Newton Keith's imprisonment in several Japanese prisoner-of-war camps from 1941 to the end of WWII. Separated from her husband and with a young son to care for she has many difficulties to face.

300453.title: Moby Dick
300453.description: When a sailor joins the crew of a whaling ship captained by a man bent on killing a white whale, he is swept up in an obsessive and fatal pursuit

301932.title: Number One
301932.description: Charlton Heston plays an aging--and deeply hurting--professional football hero who cannot accept the fact that he is through. His wife drifts away into her own life. He has an abortive affair. There is one last chance to redeem himself on the field as the fans jeer.

302148.title: The Children's Hour
302148.description: In this provocatively daring film, an attention-seeking schoolgirl vengefully spreads rumors that two of her teachers are lesbian lovers.

302248.title: A Shot In The Dark
302248.description: Peter Sellers and Elke Sommer star in this successful sequel to "The Pink Panther" in which Inspector Clouseau tries to prove a beautiful parlor maid is innocent of killing her chauffer lover.

302254.title: Solomon and Sheba
302254.description: In this biblical epic, the king of Israel proclaims which son will succeed him but a neglected brother and distant rulers threaten the new king.

302331.title: Return of the Magnificent Seven
302331.description: When a tyrant’s gunmen take all the men in a Mexican village hostage, several fighters must save the village and free its people from slave labor.

302687.title: How To Succeed In Business Without Really Trying
302687.description: With the aid of a dubious self-help book and the questionable plan that comes of it, a window washer climbs the corporate ladder in this musical.

302696.title: Lawman
302696.description: Lee J. Cobb, Robert Duvall, Robert Ryan and Burt Lancaster star in this film that reveals a deadly and truthful look at the way the West really was.

302700.title: Legend of the Lost
302700.description: A scholar, a mercenary, and a prostitute enter the Sahara Desert searching for buried treasure, but their journey soon turns sour.

302746.title: White Lightning
302746.description: A moonshine runner goes undercover to expose a corrupt sheriff and avenge the murder of his younger brother, resulting in an epic car chase.

303019.title: Where's Poppa?
303019.description: George Segal and Ruth Gordon give the funniest performances of their careers with Trish Van Devere and Rob Reiner in this black comedy about a man attempting to romance his cantankerous mother's nurse.

303020.title: The White Buffalo
303020.description: Wild Bill Hickok and Crazy Horse, two legendary figures, head out on a quest for the demon albino buffalo in this haunting western tale.

304798.title: Birdman of Alcatraz
304798.description: A steely two-time killer develops a growing love for birds while behind bars after finding an orphaned sparrow in the prison yard.

304806.title: Inherit The Wind
304806.description: Spencer Tracy and Frederic March go head-to-head as opposing attorneys in this blistering courtroom drama about the famed "Scopes Monkey Trial" where a Tennessee teacher must defend himself for teaching Darwinism.

304809.title: Support Your Local Gunfighter
304809.description: When a charming con man is mistaken for an infamous gunfighter, he decides to impersonate the gunfighter so he can earn money to pay his debts.

305018.title: I Want To Live!
305018.description: Susan Hayward won the Best Actress Oscar for her shattering portrayal of a fast-living girl who suddenly finds herself facing the death penalty for a murder she didn't commit.

305031.title: Witness For The Prosecution
305031.description: A courtroom drama about a young man on trial for a wealthy widow's murder after he suspiciously profits from her will.

305870.title: Lilies of the Field
305870.description: A warm, sensitive handyman, stranded in an Arizona desert town, builds a chapel for a lively group of nuns.

306941.title: Popi
306941.description: To give his sons a better life, a Puerto Rican widower hatches a scheme to set them adrift as Cuban refugees in a rowboat off the Florida coast.

306946.title: Run Silent, Run Deep
306946.description: With sweat-dripping realism, this taut drama stars Clark Gable as a single-minded sub commander who must contend with a tough executive officer (Burt Lancaster) and attacks from enemy forces.

307480.title: The Gallant Hours
307480.description: Based on true events, an American commander in the South Pacific during World War II makes a critical move that helps them defeat the Japanese forces.

310125.title: Clambake
310125.description: Elvis Presley rocks as a lovelorn million-heir in this sizzling comedy that features Shelley Fabares, Bill Bixby, eight new songs and bikinis galore.

310146.title: Pork Chop Hill
310146.description: After American soldiers recapture territory taken by the Chinese during the Korean War, they must prepare for a sizable attack with a depleted unit.

310154.title: 12 Angry Men
310154.description: A twelve-person jury becomes increasingly tense with arguments continuing into the night as one juror must convince the other eleven he is right.

312187.title: Midnight Cowboy
312187.description: This Academy Award-winning Best Picture features Dustin Hoffman and Jon Voight in standout roles as a con man and a Texas hustler trying to survive on the tough streets of New York.

312188.title: Mr. Majestyk
312188.description: An ex-con and Vietnam vet's attempt to run a straight business has him locking horns with both the law and the mafia in this tale of revenge.

312409.title: The Apartment
312409.description: A corporate drone hatches a scheme for success: Let the execs use his apartment for “dates.” It goes beautifully, until his love interest gets hurt.

312421.title: Marty
312421.description: Ernest Borgnine stars as Marty, a lonely Bronx butcher who gives up on love -- until he meets an equally lonely school teacher in this charming story.

334153.title: Exodus
334153.description: Following WWII, a rebel soldier helps 600 Holocaust survivors escape from British internment camps to get to Palestine, where a new nation is born.

393552.title: My Man Godfrey
393552.description: A scatterbrained socialite hires vagrant Godfrey as a butler for her eccentric family. But there's more to Godfrey than meets the eye.

441464.title: The Proud Rebel
441464.description: A Confederate veteran living in the Yankee North struggles with his son's shock induced muteness and the hate of the Northerners.

480403.title: Warlock
480403.description: A famous gunman becomes the marshal of Warlock to end a gang's rampages, but is met with opposition by a former gang member-turned-deputy sheriff.

484421.title: Woody Woodpecker
484421.description: It’s a classic cartoon cavalcade as Woody Woodpecker, Popeye, Felix The Cat, and their pals star in this family-fun movie of animated specials.

488455.title: My Name Is Nobody
488455.description: A young man attempts to convince his gunslinging idol to join him for a deadly showdown against the baddest, most dangerous men in the West.

490046.title: Popeye and Friends (Vol. 1)
490046.description: Watch as America's favorite spinach-eating sailor, and his love, Olive Oyl, outsmart the bully Bluto, and share classic adventures.

498106.title: Boots and Saddles
498106.description: When a prim English lord inherits a Western ranch, it’s up to Gene Autry and his sidekick to show him how to run the place like a real cowboy.

499218.title: 20 Million Miles to Earth
499218.description: A U.S. spaceship returning from Venus carries a horrifying lizard-like creature that has the capability to destroy an entire city.

499622.title: Operation Dames
499622.description: Four women, USO entertainers in the Korean War, try to evade alerted North Korean soldiers while trying to get back to base from behind enemy lines.

499716.title: Stagecoach
499716.description: Western classic that transcends the genre as a stagecoach carrying nine passengers through frontier wilderness faces an impending Apache attack.

506707.title: Animal Farm
506707.description: George Orwell’s classic tale of a revolution among farm animals teaches a lesson on the cost of keeping social order with an uneven power balance.

510554.title: The Roadracers
510554.description: When a race car driver’s father believes his son is to blame for a death on the track, he disowns him and sponsors a promising rival.

510560.title: Reform School Girl
510560.description: After a young woman witnesses a crime and is threatened by the guilty party, she refuses to talk to police, and is sent to a reform school.

510568.title: Daddy-O
510568.description: When a truck driver is offered a job singing in a nightclub, he quickly learns the new gig comes with some felonious strings attached.

510687.title: Motorcycle Gang
510687.description: An outlaw biker returns home after a prison stint and tries to corrupt the new straight gang leader by challenging him to an illegal street race.

511954.title: Rawhide Rangers
511954.description: Blackie's gang is creating havoc and the Ranger, Brand Calhoun and his brother go to investigate.

522136.title: Count Dracula
522136.description: Indelible performances, lush locations, and sinister sensuality mark what may be the most faithful film adaptation of Bram Stoker’s vampire classic

523586.title: The Devil's Rain
523586.description: When a cult leader is burnt alive by the local church, he vows to return and enslave the souls of the congregation’s heirs in a pact with Satan.

534189.title: Code 7, Victim 5
534189.description: A tough private eye is hired by a Cape Town millionaire after his butler is murdered. Clues about the killer soon arise in an old WWII photograph.

536857.title: The Monster Maker: The Original Schlock Classic
536857.description: A mad scientist injects his enemies with a virus which causes them to become hideously deformed.

536862.title: The Big Trees (Restored & Uncut)
536862.description: A land baron battling a Quaker colony for control of giant sequoia trees finds sharks at his heels and forms an unlikely alliance.

544522.title: The Pride of the Yankees
544522.description: From joining the New York Yankees to wedding his sweetheart to the brutal disease that would end his life, this is the story of a baseball legend.

545172.title: Broken Arrow
545172.description: Western drama about a man trying to broker peace, with dramatic consequences, between settlers and Apaches in a time of tribal mistrust.

545181.title: The Laramie Kid
545181.description: Tom attempts to stop a bank robbery, but in the process is mistaken for one of the thieves. Now, his girlfriend Peggy must prove his innocence.

545196.title: Stalag 17
545196.description: When two escaping American World War II prisoners are killed, the German P.O.W. camp barracks black marketeer is suspected of being an informer.

545825.title: Guys and Dolls
545825.description: In this musical comedy, a slick gambler with a girlfriend and a high-roller debt makes a bet with his friend to get a chilly missionary on a date.

546230.title: Blue Montana Skies
546230.description: A cattleman’s mission to a northern outpost to catch fur smugglers becomes doubly interesting when he finds a dude ranch owned by a beautiful woman.

546234.title: Red River Valley
546234.description: Singing cowboy Autry helps Arizona cattlemen try to build a dam that will bring water to their parched lands, while businessmen plot their sabotage.

547137.title: Born to the Saddle
547137.description: When an earnest young man prepares for a horse race, he’s swept up in the plans of a fiendish gambler, who hopes to manipulate the contest.

547148.title: Billy the Kid in Santa Fe
547148.description: After escaping imprisonment for a crime he didn't commit, Billy joins allies Jeff and Fuzzy to seek some good, old-fashioned justice.

548626.title: Death Valley Rangers
548626.description: Not all goes as planned when captain Ainsley sends his Trail Blazers to Death Valley to stop bandits from robbing a stagecoach of gold shipments.

548633.title: Frontier Outlaws
548633.description: Minding his own business as a gold miner, Billy’s fortunes turn south when he’s framed for murder by outlaws bullying ranchers out of their land.

548726.title: Ghost Town
548726.description: After an elderly miner is attacked by outlaws and robbed, a brave cowboy attempts to save him, and gets blamed for the crime instead.

552539.title: Law and Lawless
552539.description: A gunslinger and his pal are hired by a Spanish rancher to fight an outlaw and his gang, but the crooked foreman frames the cowboy hero for murder.

555659.title: The Lone Avenger
555659.description: When a powerful banker suddenly commits suicide, his son, the lone-riding Cal Weston, smells foul play and sets out to find his father’s killer.

556077.title: The Old Barn Dance
556077.description: A horse trader’s business and good name go belly up when a tractor company comes to town and its underhanded owner turns the residents against him.

558054.title: Toll of the Desert
558054.description: When his family is killed, a bitter cowboy becomes a ruthless hired gun, but unbeknownst to him, his son survived and is now the lawman on his trail.

559765.title: The Hound of the Baskervilles
559765.description: Sherlock Holmes and Dr. Watson investigate the legend of a supernatural hound who may be stalking a young heir on his fog-shrouded estate.

562774.title: Man From Oklahoma
562774.description: It’s up to Roy Rogers and his pioneer pals to ease a gun-toting land feud between two ranchers that was started by a grifter who wants their oil.

562817.title: Susanna Pass
562817.description: A game warden does everything he can to stop a duo with evil intentions who plan to blow up a businessman’s lake to claim the oil beneath it.

562831.title: Trigger, Jr.
562831.description: While passing through town with his traveling circus, Roy springs into action when a protection racket using a killer horse terrorizes local ranchers.

562832.title: Twilight in the Sierras
562832.description: At a home for reformed ex-convicts, parole officer Roy uncovers a counterfeit currency operation while, himself, being falsely implicated in a murder.

562851.title: Young Bill Hickok
562851.description: At the close of the Civil War, a gold shipment is stolen by foreign agents planning to assassinate President Lincoln while the wrong man is blamed.

566368.title: Fun at St Fanny's
566368.description: A 25-year-old is prevented from graduating, so his school headmaster can live off and bet with the money that the student’s uncle left in his will.

577680.title: How to Murder Your Wife
577680.description: A rich bachelor finds his swinging lifestyle ruined when he awakens one morning having married the gorgeous lady who popped out of a cake.

579461.title: Heart of Arizona
579461.description: After serving her prison sentence for standing by her outlaw husband, Belle returns home to her ranch in a hail of bullets from cattle rustlers.

579549.title: The Broken Star
579549.description: The more a deputy sheriff investigates the murder of a supposedly dangerous criminal, the more the answers point to someone he cares about deeply.

581705.title: Little Annie Rooney
581705.description: Mary Pickford wrote and stars in this lively tale of a tomboy and her big brother avenging the shooting of their policeman father.

592714.title: Zane Grey: Under the Tonto Rim
592714.description: After a band of thieves robs his stagecoach, murders the driver, and kidnaps a passenger, Brad Canfield’s revenge plot lands him in jail.

595456.title: Mule Train
595456.description: When natural cement is discovered by two prospectors, one is murdered during a claim jump attempt. Marshal Gene Autry befriends the lone prospector and tries to help him promote his cement discovery.

597657.title: Notorious
597657.description: A woman is asked to spy on a group of Nazi friends in South America. How far will she have to go to ingratiate herself with them?

599223.title: Hercules
599223.description: The muscular Hercules performs his Labors, sails with the Argonauts, and romances the fair Iole.

601252.title: McLintock!
601252.description: A cattle baron with the diplomatic savvy to keep peace between dueling power brokers in town can’t seem to get his wife and daughter under control.

601961.title: The Incredibly Strange Creatures Who Stopped Living and Became Zombies
601961.description: After a bizarre encounter at a carnival, a man is lulled into a hypnotic trance and turns into a mindless, bloodthirsty killing machine.

602919.title: Sudden Fear
602919.description: A successful playwright comes to discover the masked motives of her new struggling actor husband for marrying her — and love isn’t one of them.

602929.title: Jet Storm
602929.description: A revenge plot for his daughter’s murder at the hands of a hit-and-run driver sends a man on a commercial flight from London to New York with a bomb.

602963.title: El Inspector General (Doblado)
602963.description: A un estafador lo confunden con el enviado oficial del emperador Napoleon Bonaparte para combatir la corrupción generalizada que reina en Francia.

603960.title: Fort Algiers
603960.description: A spy posing as a nightclub singer gains the confidence of a suspected rebel leader who is feared to be leading an uprising to control oil fields of Algeria.

603981.title: The Crooked Way
603981.description: John Payne plays Eddie Rice, a man who's just gotten out of a veteran's  hospital where they removed a piece of shrapnel from his brain. And his memory. He goes back to Los Angeles to find out who he was before he went to war. Turns out he was a gangster. Stepping out of the train station he's arrested by the police as someone who was warned to stay out of town long ago. A girl on the street recognizes him as her ex-husband and makes it very clear she hates his guts. A gang leader beats the daylights out of him for an old double-cross. Welcome home, Eddie. Main plot gets under-way when the gang leader kills a detective and tries to pin the rap on Eddie. Eddie takes a lot of punishment in this one.

603995.title: God's Little Acre
603995.description: The primitive, ribald Georgia rustics of Erskine Caldwell's best-selling novel are brought brilliantly to the screen in the widely acclaimed American classic. Provocative for it's day, the frank and sexy novel has lost none of it's zest in this transformation to celluloid. In fact, the changes necessitated by the nature of movie-making may have made it better. Robert Ryan, in what many critics claim as the role of his career, plays Ty Ty Walden, the poor white farmer convinced that there is a golden treasure buried somewhere on his land. He spends years digging up the farm, littering the fields with empty holes, in his fruitless quest for riches. His family and his share-croppers languish in poverty. The 'Little Acre' referred to in the title is that bit of land set aside as an offering to the church. But in the simple and direct way of country folk, the acre is moveable if it is thought to contain the treasure. It's not sacrilege or disrespect but the honest bargain of a simple man with his God. His struggle for an easy answer to life's problems is mirrored in the actions of the rest of the cast, each one believing in something seemingly impossible to achieve. It is a terrific ensemble cast in support of Ryan, all responding ably to the firm direction of Anthony Mann.

607423.title: High Lonesome
607423.description: In Big Bend Country in Texas, a recent spate of unsolved murders get pinned on a mysterious young drifter in town who gets caught up with bad actors.

611471.title: The Giant of Marathon
611471.description: Set in 490 B.C., this is the dramatic tale of a Greek soldier who gathers the courage and manpower to lead a battle against the invading Persian army.

612058.title: La Batalla De Maraton (Doblado)
612058.description: Ante la amenaza de invasión del ejército persa durante las Guerras Médicas, un soldado griego encabeza la valiente defensa de su nación.

612822.title: The Black Pirate
612822.description: Douglas Fairbanks created a new breed of onscreen hero in this 1926 silent film classic about a man infiltrating a pirate ship for personal revenge.

613757.title: Hercules Conquers Atlantis
613757.description: The intrepid Greek hero rescues a maiden from the clutches of an evil creature and goes on to save his son from the sexist queen of lost Atlantis.

614247.title: Loan Shark
614247.description: In this film noir, an ex-convict, now on the right side of the law, infiltrates a group of loan sharks that  preys upon desperate factory workers.

614634.title: Goliath and the Dragon (Vengeance of Hercules)
614634.description: Returning home, the mythical muscleman finds new enemies in his own kingdom in the form of giant bats, three-headed dogs, and a vicious dragon.

615524.title: Apache Country
615524.description: When a bad guy tries to control Native Americans by getting them drunk, cavalry scout Autry must break up a ring which uses raids to cover up crimes.

615528.title: Night Stage to Galveston
615528.description: Gene Autry and Pat Buttram work for a newspaper publisher, and find evidence of corruption in the Texas State Police.

615627.title: El Ángel Y El Pistolero (Doblado)
615627.description: Quirt Evans, un chico malo en todos los aspectos, conoce a Penélope, una chica cuáquera y debe elegir entre su mundo y el mundo en el que vive ella.

615656.title: Esther Y El Rey (Doblado)
615656.description: Esther (una judía) llama la atención del rey Asuero, que acaba de enviudar y esta tratando de sofocar y derrotar la campaña de odio contra los judíos.

616416.title: Atlas en La Tierra De Los Ciclopes (Doblado)
616416.description: Una joven se convierte en víctima de una vieja maldición que cae sobre la familia y en su noche de bodas es violada por un fantasma y queda embarazada.

622110.title: It Can Be Done Amigo
622110.description: Two unlikely outlaws – one a fist-fighting drifter and the other a gunslinging pimp – help a child claim his inheritance without getting swindled.

623870.title: Sparrows: 4k Restoration
623870.description: The eldest resident at a farm for children of unwed mothers fights to keep her young friends safe from the clutches of a wicked master.

628942.title: The Colditz Story
628942.description: British, French, Dutch, and Polish POWs join forces to plan their getaways from an “escape-proof” medieval castle and prove their Nazi captors wrong.

632222.title: The French Way
632222.description: In WWII France, a cabaret star steps in to help a young pair of star-crossed lovers whose feuding families have forbidden them to get married.

632226.title: Two-Gun Man From Harlem
632226.description: When a murder is wrongly pinned on a straight-shooting cowpoke, he heads to Harlem and infiltrates a gang to sniff out the men who framed him.

632974.title: Siren of the Tropics
632974.description: Legendary Josephine Baker stars in this silent film as a woman who falls for the man who saved her life and finds out he’s engaged to someone else.

633118.title: Apasionadamente (Doblado)
633118.description: Un circo americano buscando mejores perspectivas se instala en Alemania y se convierte en el escenario para el pecado, el sexo y el melodrama.

636895.title: Batman
636895.description: After the Pearl Harbor attack, a pair of costumed secret agents are tasked with foiling a Japanese spy’s plan to mind-control American scientists.

641152.title: The Bridge of San Luis Rey
641152.description: When a rope bridge collapses in 18th century Peru and kills five tourists, a Franciscan monk is tried by the Inquisition for investigating the cause.

641185.title: The Stranger Wore a Gun
641185.description: After the Civil War, a spy for the Confederacy absconds to Arizona to start a new life but gets reluctantly pulled into a stagecoach gold robbery.

641665.title: El Miedo No Anda en Burro
641665.description: La India María hereda una fortuna de su patrón que falleció. Los parientes del finado recurrirán a una serie de planes para recuperar la fortuna.

642232.title: Four Faces West
642232.description: When a New Mexico cowpoke holds a banker at gunpoint to get an unsecured loan, offering an IOU, he must flee from the local marshal and his posse.

642235.title: Terror at Black Falls
642235.description: A Mexican gunslinger, unjustly imprisoned for trying to save his son from a lynch mob, is released and seeks revenge. But is his target the wrong man?

643081.title: West Side Story
643081.description: This electrifying musical, winner of ten Academy Awards, including Best Picture, reimagines “Romeo and Juliet,” set during gang warfare in 1950s NYC.

644877.title: Rio Lobo
644877.description: A former Union officer teams up with ex-Confederate rebels to find a traitor who caused the death of a close friend and now runs a lawless Texas town.

644879.title: Big Jake
644879.description: When his grandson is kidnapped, the feisty head of his estranged family goes home, supposedly to deliver the ransom, but intending to put up a fight.

646730.title: Fists of Fury
646730.description: A kung-fu fighter discovers the ice factory where he works is a front for the same drug trafficking ring responsible for the deaths of his relatives.

646736.title: They Call Me Trinity
646736.description: A bounty hunter and his outlaw brother become the goofy gunslinging duo standing in the way of a craven landowner’s plan to run out Mormon settlers.

646737.title: Trinity Is Still My Name
646737.description: In the process of honoring their father’s dying wish to become famous Old West outlaws, a pair of gunslinging brothers turn into do-gooders instead.

654634.title: La Hija De Frankenstein (Doblado)
654634.description: Cuando el doctor Frankenstein es asesinado por un monstruo que creó, su hija trasplanta el cerebro de su asistente y amante en otro cuerpo más jóven.

655196.title: La Reina De Nueva York (Doblado)
655196.description: Una mujer se entera de que no se está muriendo de intoxicación por radiacion, pero finge estar enferma para aparecer en un reportaje.

658216.title: Combat!: Mail Call
658216.description: Sgt. Saunders' squad blames his bad treatment of a likable new member on his foul mood. But really, Saunders believes the soldier is faking injuries.

658226.title: Return to Paradise
658226.description: After washing up on a Pacific island controlled by a puritanical missionary, a drifter challenges the despot and carves out a life with the locals.

658239.title: The Green Promise
658239.description: A stubborn farmer fears the modern forces that could change his family as one of his daughters pursues romance and another seeks to join the 4-H club.

658241.title: Thunder Road
658241.description: A veteran returns home to the mountains to take over the family moonshining business, but soon runs into trouble from big-city gangsters and the law.

660344.title: Go, Man, Go!
660344.description: This film portrays the story of a Jewish basketball coach, Abe Saperstein, and the creation of the famous Harlem Globetrotters in the 1920s.

667841.title: North of the Rio Grande
667841.description: When the brother of cowboy hero Hopalong Cassidy is murdered, he hatches a scheme to catch those responsible by posing as a wanted man.

669275.title: Son of Cleopatra
669275.description: In Roman-occupied ancient Egypt, the corrupt administration of the governor sparks a revolt led by Cleopatra's son, El Kabir.

670302.title: Cavalry Command
670302.description: In 1902, an American cavalry platoon is sent to aid a Philippine town, where they must quiet rebel leader who refuses to accept that the war is over.

671834.title: Heritage of the Desert
671834.description: When an engaged woman falls in love with a wounded man that her family is caring for, she flees her wedding and finds herself held hostage by outlaws.

673781.title: Away All Boats
673781.description: During the Second World War, a group of Allied sailors board an old warship to transfer an infantry battalion to various parts of the Pacific.

674399.title: The Fast and the Furious
674399.description: Frank Webster is on the run from a framed murder charge when he meets Connie. The two begin to fall for each other, and now Frank must clear his name.

675193.title: The First Time
675193.description: A trio of teenage boys enter a go-go bar and meet a beautiful woman. However, she has her own agenda… and she needs them as much as they want her.

679440.title: The Man From Cairo
679440.description: An ex-G.I. who served in Algeria during World War II and returns as a tourist is mistaken for a spy for the French government to recover stolen gold.

679457.title: The Wrong Road
679457.description: A bank heist pulled off by one of its tellers and his fiancé leads the couple, an ex-cell mate and a detective on a wild ride to a $100,000 bounty.

679465.title: Sheriff of Sage Valley
679465.description: On the run, Billy and his posse take cover in a small town in Sage Valley where he becomes sheriff and the target of a local gang of outlaws.

679540.title: Saga of Death Valley
679540.description: In 1895, 15 years after his father was gunned down in cold blood and his toddler brother was kidnapped, Roy sets out for revenge and a reunion.

680016.title: Shanty Tramp
680016.description: The local "tramp" begins to make waves in the community when she turns down a sleazy evangelist. Upset, he makes sure this doesn't go without trouble.

680753.title: The Naked Hills
680753.description: A farmer in 1849 Indiana who catches a case of gold fever makes the cross-country trek to find the ‘mother lode’ hidden in the Californian hills.

681343.title: The Avenger
681343.description: Aeneas leads escapees from the Trojan war to new land in Italy and must deal with new threats to his people, such as the army commanded by King Turno.

681408.title: El Espectro (Sub Esp)
681408.description: Una mujer y su amante asesinan a su marido. Pronto, sin embargo, empiezan a ocurrir cosas extrañas, y se preguntan si realmente lo mataron.

682049.title: Charada "La Farsa" (Doblado)
682049.description: Romance y suspenso en París. Una viuda es perseguida por varios hombres que quieren la fortuna que le había robado su marido asesinado.

682401.title: Clearing the Range
682401.description: In this Zorro-like hero film, Curt Fremont poses in public as a coward but transforms into the daring El Capitan while hunting his brother’s killer.

682403.title: The Dude Bandit
682403.description: When a man's murder is made to look like a suicide, investigator Ace Cooper poses as a coward during the day but becomes Dude Bandit at night.

682788.title: La Leyenda De Eneas (Doblado)
682788.description: Eneas lleva a los fugitivos de la guerra de Troya a nuevas tierras en Italia y debe enfrentarse a nuevas amenazas para su pueblo.

682992.title: Charade
682992.description: Before she can finalize her divorce, Regina Lampert’s husband turns up dead and she soon finds herself pursued in Paris for the fortune he’d stolen.

683054.title: The Fighting Westerner
683054.description: When a murderer begins taking down the heirs to a valuable radium mine, a mining engineer attempts to find the killer and clear his cousin's name.

688135.title: Hercules and the Tyrants of Babylon
688135.description: The mighty and mythical warrior fights to free the enslaved people of Babylon from the rule of the dead king’s three equally sadistic heirs.

688621.title: El Lago De Satán (Doblado)
688621.description: Un turista recién casado y un conde de Transilvania deben trabajar juntos cuando la esposa del primero se convierte en la huésped de una bruja.

688622.title: Hercules Encadenado (Doblado)
688622.description: Mientras negocia la paz entre dos hermanos que disputan el trono de Tebas, un Hercules amnesico es seducido por la malvada reina Omphale.

688624.title: Hercules Contra Los Tiranos De Babilonia (Doblado)
688624.description: Peter Lupus protagoniza el papel de Hércules en este opus italiano. Hercules lucha para liberar al pueblo de Babilonia de una hechicera malvada.

689001.title: She Beast
689001.description: A newlywed tourist and an eccentric Transylvanian Count must work together when the former's beautiful wife finds herself the bodily host of a witch.

689650.title: The Pink Panther
689650.description: The bumbling Inspector Jacques Clouseau tries to catch an infamous jewel thief before he can steal a priceless diamond from a princess.

689652.title: In the Heat of the Night
689652.description: While traveling in the deep south, a black Philadelphian homicide detective becomes embroiled in a murder investigation.

690168.title: The Man From the Diners' Club
690168.description: After mistakenly issuing a credit card to a notorious mafioso, a Diners Club rep must take on the dangerous task of getting it back to keep his job.

690214.title: Hand in Hand
690214.description: A 7-year-old Roman Catholic boy and his Jewish female schoolmate become unlikely best friends despite the religious prejudice that surrounds them.

693536.title: Duke of the Navy
693536.description: When two sailors take a much-needed break on land, they manage to get mixed up in a game of girls, gangsters, and buried treasure.

694668.title: The Mistress of Atlantis
694668.description: Amid the shifting sands of the Sahara Desert, two French Foreign Legionnaires discover a subterranean passage to a lost world ruled by an evil queen.

695986.title: One-Eyed Jacks
695986.description: After robbing a Mexican bank, Dad Longworth takes the loot and leaves his partner Rio to be captured, but finds a target on his back when Rio escapes.

697997.title: The Joe Louis Story
697997.description: This film follows the life and career of heavyweight champion Joe Louis, who battled opponents inside the ring and racism outside it.

698029.title: The Beatniks
698029.description: A chance encounter with a talent agent leads a gifted singer and secret gang leader to a record contract that gets undermined by his hoodlum friends.

698087.title: Zulu
698087.description: Counting only 100 among their ranks, outnumbered British soldiers do battle with 4,000 Zulu warriors at the 1879 Battle of Rorke's Drift.

705216.title: Colonel Effingham's Raid
705216.description: At the dawn of America's entry into World War II, a retired Army colonel rallies his small Southern town against renaming its Confederate Square.

705448.title: Mr. Topaze
705448.description: After realizing he's become a pawn in a corrupt politician's crooked business, the remarkably honest Mr. Topaze decides to swindle his manipulators.

707724.title: The Devil-Ship Pirates
707724.description: A damaged privateer deserts the Spanish Armada and makes land for repairs near a village on the British coast where he terrorizes the locals.

708740.title: Julius Caesar
708740.description: When Julius Caesar's growing ambition begins to worry his friend Brutus, Brutus is easily persuaded to participate in a plot to assassinate Caesar.

713711.title: Luna Nueva (Doblado)
713711.description: El editor de un periódico utiliza todos los trucos del libro para evitar que su exesposa, una destacada reportera, se vuelva a casar.

713734.title: Hasta Que Las Nubes Pasen (Doblado)
713734.description: Jerome Kern, pionero de Broadway es incapaz de encontrar un éxito inmediato en Estados Unidos, pero en Inglaterra sus sueños de éxito se hacen realidad.

713800.title: El Extraño (Doblado)
713800.description: Un investigador de la Comisión de Crímenes de Guerra viaja a Connecticut para encontrar a un infame nazi.

713903.title: The Body Stealers
713903.description: When NATO paratroopers are being snatched during routine jumps by a mysterious red beam of alien origin, the military launches an investigation.

715573.title: Buffalo Bill: Hero of the West
715573.description: In order to avoid an all-out war, Buffalo Bill finds himself looking to stop an illegal arms trade perpetuated by Big Sam Dolandson.

723259.title: El Libro De La Selva (Doblado)
723259.description: Secuestrado y obligado a vivir con humanos, un joven inicia una cadena de eventos cuando encuentra el tesoro maldito de un rey muerto.

723961.title: The Mystery of the Hooded Horsemen
723961.description: Tex becomes a victim of mistaken identity after he and his sidekick go up against a gang of masked riders terrorizing the owners of a gold mine.

100000154.title: Affair in Monte Carlo
100000154.description: A café owner regales his patrons with a story about a well-heeled widow’s 24-hour fling with a compulsive gambler on the French Riviera.

100001513.title: Meeting at Midnight
100001513.description: After a murder occurs during a séance, Charlie Chan must search for the killer amidst the numerous ghosts conjured up by a motley crew of mediums.

100001605.title: The Thing From Another World
100001605.description: After retrieving a body from a crashed flying saucer, scientists fend off a bloodthirsty alien organism at a remote research facility in the Arctic.

100001762.title: Confessions of a Psycho Cat
100001762.description: A sociopathic socialite offers three acquitted murderers $100,000 if they can stay alive for 24 hours while she hunts them down through New York City.

100003063.title: Hacha De Guerra (Doblado)
100003063.description: Un artista que trabaja en el remoto Fort Alden se debate entre su amor por dos mujeres y la guerra entre los nativos americanos y los Estados Unidos.

0300009663.title: The Adventures of Ozzie and Harriet
0300009663.description: A clean-cut 1950’s couple raises their two sons through life’s growing pains as they tackle issues surrounding teenage-hood, marriage and career.

0300010230.title: My Favorite Martian
0300010230.description: After his spaceship crash lands in Los Angeles, a human-looking martian finds himself befriended by a reporter who takes him under his wing.

0300007499.title: One Step Beyond
0300007499.description: As an extension of the tradition of radio horror dramas, this program sought out and re-created real stories of the supernatural for each episode.

0300000125.title: Welcome Back, Kotter
0300000125.description: This series follows teacher Gabe Kotter as he returns to his former high school to teach a remedial class of students known as the “Sweathogs.”

0300009053.title: Alfred Hitchcock Presents
0300009053.description: This series of unrelated short stories covers people of different backgrounds committing murders, thefts, and crimes caused by particular motivations.

0300009167.title: Wagon Train
0300009167.description: Follow the adventures of a wagon train as it travels through the plains, deserts, and mountains on its way from post-Civil War Missouri to California.
